r 2-column layout. The left column will house active sandbox environments, AI operations, and telemetry analytics, while the right column will hold recommended actions and system logs.\n\n\n**Refining CTA Card Design**\n\nI'm now refining the CTA card design for the dashboard, focusing on a premium look. I've designed a \"Sovereign Security Enclave\" CTA card with a neon blue border, dark gradient background, and a concise message to improve the UI. This uses `WorkspaceCard` components and `lucide-react` icons. I'm also implementing a specific bento layout.\n\n\n\n**Enhancing Enclave CTA**\n\nI'm now integrating the CTA card for enclave spin-up. I've successfully incorporated the \"Sovereign Security Enclave\" CTA card with the neon blue border and dark background using `WorkspaceCard`. I am adding the request enclave spin-up feature to improve usability. Furthermore, I've designed and added a dedicated info bar for a premium welcome banner or disclaimer notification, for a better UI.\n\n\n**Adding Mock-Data Telemetry**\n\nI'm working on integrating the demo environment banner. I've decided to add the `PreviewTelemetryBanner` with warning and status, and have the components mapped to the design architecture and data mapping. I'm focusing on making a clear and understandable mock-data disclaimer to improve overall usability.\n\n\n\n**Validating Imports & Names**\n\nI'm now validating all imports to check for duplicate declarations. I've re-reviewed the component names and import statements, verifying consistency and naming conventions, ensuring that there are no overlaps. I'm prioritizing overall stability.\n\n\n**Exploring Enhanced Cockpit Elements**\n\nI'm now exploring potential enhancements for a more premium dashboard experience, and verifying if all the components from `/components/private-app` are imported correctly. I'm considering a \"Narrative Timeline\" or \"Operating Model Diagram\" to further elevate the cockpit's strategic design.\n\n\n**Visualizing Enc